wikipedia_page.main: Nathan Blissett (born 29 June 1990) is an English professional footballer who plays as a forward for National League club Maidenhead United. He has also made appearances for Kidderminster Harriers, Cambridge United, Bristol Rovers, Tranmere Rovers, Torquay United, Plymouth Argyle, Macclesfield Town and Solihull Moors.
